channel.title: Server Error
channel.description:
Alright thanks for clicking this in a first place and reading this. I've got a friend running a server (well attempting to but it's currently not running) He's looking for help he made a topic on another forum. Nobody was able to help so i suggested Mopar, trusting my gut you guys maybe are more helpful. This is his explanation, I don't understand it as I dont know errors you get.
"Hey guys..so i got those errors client & server sided that i just cant get to work.. can anyone help me fix them teamviewing? and also maybe help me add one quick thing cuz i find it kinda hard? add me on skype or post yours here
Daniel-shadyy"
If anyones willing to help him with a 317 Server add his skype: Daniel-shadyy
Thanks in advanced to anyone able to help him with his problem.
